      <h1>Release Notes</h1>

      <p>These release notes are in reverse chronological order.</p>
      <h2>Latest Version</h2>
      <p>Head of CVS</p>
      <h3>ROOTIO</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Added latest version of ROOTIO.</li>
      </ul>
      <h3>VectorGraphics</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Fixed a problem with curved shapes in the SWF format. FreeHEP-74</li>
        <li>Added imaging (including transparency) to the SWF format.
        It also handled setPaint(TexturePaint) now.
        FreeHEP-24, FreeHEP-119 and FreeHEP-171</li>
        <li>Fixed PrintColor class to rely on JDK 1.4 Color constants.</li>
        <li>Added WebColor class to create Colors following the 216-web color
        scheme.</li>
        <li>The drawSymbol and fillSymbol methods in PixelGraphics2D will use
        image blitting of cached symbol images of max size 32x32, in the case
        the display is local (Windows32, MacOSX and X11local). In the X11 Remote
        case normal drawing procedures are used. The colors are converted to
        WebColors. For VectorGraphics export everything stays as normal.</li>
      </ul>
      <h2>Version 1.1 (March 20, 2003)</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Initial public release.</li>
      </ul>

